rpreter EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n85: test -f docs/docs/api/cli.md && echo \"cli EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n86: \n87: # Verify new CRD docs (expected after tasks)\n88: test -f docs/docs/api/crd-agentruntime.md && echo \"crd-agentruntime EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n89: test -f docs/docs/api/crd-codeinterpreter.md && echo \"crd-codeinterpreter EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n90: ```\n91: \n92: ---\n93: \n94: ## Dependencies\n95: \n96: - T-002 requires access to `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` source code\n97: - T-004 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/templates/crd-agentruntime.yaml`\n98: - T-005 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/templates/crd-codeinterpreter.yaml`\n99: - T-006 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n100: \n101: ---\n102: \n103: *Stage ST-3 completed*\n\n(End of file - total 103 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043 — Architecture Design Documents & API Documentation\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-043\n- **Module**: docs\n- **Language**: Markdown\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-3 Completed (tasks.md creation)\n\n## Pre-check\n\n- [ ] Verify existing architecture.md at `docs/docs/guides/architecture.md`\n- [ ] Verify existing API docs at `docs/docs/api/agent-runtime.md`\n- [ ] Verify existing CLI docs at `docs/docs/api/cli.md`\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Architecture Design Document\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-043/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775888188911,"end":1775888188932}}}}
